### Python ###
# Bytecode and cache files generated during execution
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

### Media & Large Data ###
# Large video and data files (Avoid uploading to GitHub due to size limits)
*.mp4
*.avi
*.mov
data/

### Environments ###
# Python virtual environments (Dependencies should be managed via requirements.txt)
venv/
.env

### IDE / Editors ###
# Editor-specific configurations (VS Code, PyCharm, etc.)
.vscode/
.idea/

### System Files ###
# OS-specific metadata files (macOS/Windows junk)
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db